commit.message: Moved pypi production deploy to travis instead of in release.sh
Fixed a case where argument on the newline that started with def (like 'default') where recognised as a method definition.
Moved to checking only decorated methods and methods for a newline
From physical lines to logical lines to give classes with multiple bases on the newline a pass
Added GitHub URL to package setup
Updated the README with an example of why to use this plugin
Updated a test that I'd forgotten to update
Added support for ignoring docstring on the newline after a class definition, as per pep8
Fixed an issue where the line numbers of one file would bleed into the second file, therefore eventually producing errors on every line
Completely rewrote the line checker into a flake8 check function instead of an AST tree class
Added the option to ignore docstrings directly under a class definition
Updated python version in tox to match compatibility
Updated release script to work with twine
